Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.49,0:22:27.41,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}無人在意
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.41,0:22:29.99,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}便無人在意
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.99,0:22:33.70,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}為何偏被你拾起
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.25,0:22:41.25,ED_CH_EP02,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}仿若難得一見的珍奇
